t("worm that walks out of sight", "蠕虫合体在视野外", "_t")
t("Shared Insanity", "共享疯狂", "_t")
t("Linked to their horror ally gaining %d%% all damage resistance.", "和恐魔建立链接，获得 %d%% 全体伤害抗性。", "tformat")
