t("Writhing Hairs", "苦痛之发", "_t")
t("Half turned to stone, reducing movement speed by %d%% and 35%% chances to shatter on damage, increasing damge taken by %d%%.", "半石化中，移动速度降低 %d%%，35%% 几率增加 %d%% 受到的伤害。", "tformat")
